OL,3,C'This isn't Castlereagh': Ministers
OL,4,Cwarned over answering questions
OL,6,FThe Northern Ireland Assembly Speaker
OL,7,Fissued a stark warning to Executive
OL,8,Fministers to be more open with answers
OL,9,Ffor the sake of devolution.
OL,11,FIn his latest caution to members,
OL,12,FEdwin Poots responded to a point of
OL,13,Forder from DUP MLA Philip Brett.
OL,15,FMr Brett asked the Justice Minister to
OL,16,Fdetail the amount spent to date by the
OL,17,FPolice Ombudsman as a result of legal
OL,18,Faction taken by the Northern Ireland
OL,19,FRetired Police Officers Association.
