OL,6,FHe said the written response he
OL,7,Freceived on Monday from the Justice
OL,8,FMinister said that the matter was an
OL,9,Foperational one for the Office of the
OL,10,FPolice Ombudsman
OL,12,FA spokesperson said: "The Department
OL,13,Fof Justice does not hold the
OL,14,Finformation requested.
OL,16,F"The Police Ombudsman's Office is a
OL,17,Fnon-departmental public body, which
OL,18,Freceives an annual budget from the
OL,19,FDepartment of Justice. Its expenditure
OL,20,Ffalls under the remit of the Police
OL,21,FOmbudsman's Accounting Officer.
