OL,3,C'This isn't Castlereagh': Ministers
OL,4,Cwarned over answering questions
OL,6,F"This isn't Castlereagh Holding Centre
OL,7,Fwhere people are sitting saying no
OL,8,Fcomment, no comment, no comment.
OL,10,F"I would suggest to ministers that
OL,11,Fit's not a good look withholding
OL,12,Finformation from members where you
OL,13,Fhave that information and I will do my
OL,14,Futmost as speaker to ensure that
OL,15,Fmembers get the answers to questions
OL,16,Fand hold ministers to account, because
OL,17,Fthat is the role of this body in this
OL,18,Fbuilding - it is to hold people who
OL,19,Fare making decisions on your behalf to
OL,20,Faccount.
