OL,3,C'This isn't Castlereagh': Ministers
OL,4,Cwarned over answering questions
OL,6,F"There's no point in having devolution
OL,7,Fif we can't hold our ministers and
OL,8,FExecutive to account."
OL,10,FCastlereagh Holding Centre in east
OL,11,FBelfast was one of the RUC's main
OL,12,Finterrogation centres for those
OL,13,Fsuspected of terrorist offences. It
OL,14,Fwas closed in 1999 as part of
OL,15,Frecommendations into policing reform
OL,16,Fin Northern Ireland.
OL,18,FMr Poots' rebuke comes after he
OL,19,Freminded MLAs of the dress code las
OL,20,Fmonth urging them to "dress smartly"
OL,21,Fin the chamber.
