OL,3,C'This isn't Castlereagh': Ministers
OL,4,Cwarned over answering questions
OL,6,FIn a letter to all MLAs, Mr Poots said
OL,7,Fsome had been "discourteous" by not
OL,8,Fbeing in place in the chamber when
OL,9,Fcalled to ask a question, and that he
OL,10,Fwould have "more to say" about the
OL,11,Fstandards of debate in the chamber in
OL,12,Fthe coming weeks.
OL,14,FEarlier this month, Mr Poots said it
OL,15,Fis "out of order" for MLAs to claim he
OL,16,Fand others in the chair make political
OL,17,Fdecisions.
